---
// src/pages/index.astro
---
<title> baldi's basics online</title>
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg"/>

<!-- Navbar -->
<nav class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-purple-800 to-indigo-600 text-white p-4 shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-40">
  <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
    <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-bold text-white-400 hover:text-white-300 transition-all duration-300">Baldi's Basics Online</a>
    <div class="flex space-x-6">
      <!-- Links with smooth scroll -->
      <a href="#play" class="text-lg px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:text-gray-800 transition-all duration-300" data-scroll="play">Play</a>
      <a href="#credits" class="text-lg px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:text-gray-800 transition-all duration-300" data-scroll="credits">Credits</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Gameplay Section -->
<section id="play" class="container mx-auto py-16">
  <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-6">Play Baldi's Basics Online</h2>
  <p class="text-center mb-6 text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    Step into the world of Baldi's Basics in this browser version! Test your math skills, explore the school, and avoid Baldi as you collect notebooks. This is a port of the original game, designed to run in your browser.
  </p>
  <!-- IFrame Section -->
  <div class="relative w-full h-[800px] md:h-[1000px] bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
    <iframe
      src="/baldi.html"
      class="w-full h-full border-none"
      id="baldi-iframe"
      allowfullscreen
    ></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-6">
    <button
      onclick="document.getElementById('baldi-iframe').requestFullscreen()"
      class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 shadow-lg transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
    >
      Full-Screen Mode
    </button>
  </div>
  <p class="text-center mt-2 text-gray-500">
    For the best experience, try playing in full-screen mode.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Credits Section -->
<section id="credits" class="container mx-auto py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 via-gray-700 to-gray-600 rounded-lg shadow-xl">
  <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-6">Credits</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-white">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Micah McGonigal</h3>
      <p>Creator of the original Baldi's Basics game. Micah's quirky concept of a horror game disguised as an educational tool has captivated players worldwide.</p>
      <div class="mt-2">
        <a href="https://basicallygames.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-all duration-300">Official Website</a><br>
        <a href="https://mystman12.itch.io/baldis-basics" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-all duration-300">itch.io</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">CyndaquilDAC</h3>
      <p>The genius behind this WebGL version of Baldi's Basics. Thanks to CyndaquilDAC, you can now enjoy the game directly in your browser.</p>
      <div class="mt-2">
        <a href="https://github.com/CyndaquilDAC" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-all duration-300">GitHub</a><br>
        <a href="https://baldis-basics.fandom.com/wiki/User:CyndaquilDAC" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-all duration-300">Wiki Profile</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Meta Game Jam</h3>
      <p>The jam that started it all. Baldi's Basics was born here, and the world of surreal educational horror was forever changed.</p>
      <div class="mt-2">
        <a href="https://itch.io/jam/metagamejam/rate/239841" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-all duration-300">Submission Page</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Client-Side Script for Smooth Scrolling -->
<script type="module">
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-scroll]').forEach((link) => {
    link.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
      event.preventDefault();
      const targetId = link.getAttribute('data-scroll');
      const targetElement = document.getElementById(targetId);
      if (targetElement) {
        targetElement.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
      } else {
        console.error(`Section with ID "${targetId}" not found.`);
      }
    });
  });
</script>
